2 Introduction This is a report for an experiment that was undertaken during an undergradaute chemistry course, that focuses on the Gringnard Reaction.

3 Aims To form a Gringnard reagent in situ, react it with methyl benzoate and then do a reaction ‘work up’ to produce the final product of triphenylmethanol and test the product with a melting point and Infra Red spectrum.
